## Error Responses

All errors follow this format:
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Error description"
}
```

**Common Status Codes:**
- `400` - Bad Request (missing/invalid data)
- `401` - Unauthorized (missing/invalid token)
- `404` - Not Found
- `500` - Internal Server Error

